{"tid":1090390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★$4000】收到大批市民求助，指遞交申請表後仍未收到通知而感到恐慌","createTime":"2019-04-03T12:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T03:58:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea105ccfe8b05eb52ac4ff860807fc0d49f5d524","tid":1090390,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"關愛共享計劃自今年2月接受申請已頻頻甩轆，包括表格派罄、熱線冧檔及「要攞銀紙先備白紙」等，令各政黨地區人士要忙為政府補鑊。在過去2個月內，有政黨收到大批市民求助，指遞交申請表後仍未收到通知而感到恐慌，加上致電熱線又不獲回覆，多名立法會議員遂約見財庫局局長劉怡翔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403110922466-0403_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fbkn-20190403110922466-0403_00822_001.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5PS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=9183142f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403110922466-0403_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1807ba450e5de5512bba90abc6feb44fca84a0b6","tid":1090390,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"極度恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf99283a2ad79cb5eb74155199f143220cfdf08","tid":1090390,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b09b29fb50f4534573114a5617a4d8456c6a51","tid":1090390,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"my money<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a